      <h2>World's most liveable city</h2>

      <div class="outro">
        <p>
          Munich is a major centre of art, technology, finance, publishing,
          culture, innovation, education, business, and tourism in Europe and
          enjoys a very high standard and quality of living, reaching first in
          Germany and third worldwide according to the 2018 Mercer survey, and
          being rated the world's most liveable city by the Monocle's Quality of
          Life Survey 2018. According to the Globalization and World Rankings
          Research Institute Munich is considered an alpha-world city, as of
          2015.
        </p>
      </div>

